Core Tables

users – login credentials, username, password, role (ADMIN/DRIVER/STUDENT)

admins – admin-specific info (name, contact, email)

drivers – driver personal info, license, contact, profile image

students – personal info, bus assignment, class, QR code, fee status, transport validation

student_parents – parent info, relation, contact, email

Transport & Scheduling

buses – bus number, capacity, type, assigned driver

routes – route name, start/end, total stops

stops – stop name, GPS coordinates

route_stops – mapping route ↔ stops, stop order

schedules – bus schedule: route, driver, timing

bus_assignments – history of driver ↔ bus assignments

Logs & QR Tracking

qr_logs – QR scan events, student validation, timestamp, status

trip_logs – trip start/end, driver, bus, route, timing

alerts – invalid QR, fee due, absence, etc.

notifications – SMS/WhatsApp alerts sent, status, message content

Finance & Fee

fee_transactions – student fee payment info, mode, status, date

Driver & Vehicle Management

driver_attendance – daily attendance, leave, remarks

vehicle_maintenance – maintenance records, costs, status

Admin & Audit

admin_logs – actions by admin, timestamp, description

Optional / Advanced Tables

student_attendance – overall attendance by day/class/bus

events – any school/transport events for notifications

complaints_feedback – student/parent complaints, feedback

gps_tracking – bus GPS coordinates history for tracking

user_roles – role management (for future JWT/permission system)

qr_templates – QR code generation template/versioning

sms_templates – predefined messages for parent alerts

school_info – school/college details, contact, logo, etc.


